summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2011 TOYOTA SIENNA. THE CONTACT STATED THAT THE POWER SLIDING DOOR FAILED TO AUTOMATICALLY OPEN OR CLOSE. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT TAKEN TO A DEALER OR INDEPENDENT MECHANIC FOR DIAGNOSTIC TESTING. THE CONTACT RECEIVED NOTIFICATION OF NHTSA CAMPAIGN NUMBER: 16V858000 (STRUCTURE); HOWEVER, THE PARTS FOR THE RECALL REPAIR WERE NOT AVAILABLE. THE CONTACT STATED THAT BUTLER TOYOTA (3232 HARPER RD, INDIANAPOLIS, IN 16240, (844) 829-9600) INFORMED THE CONTACT THAT PARTS WERE NOT AVAILABLE. THE CONTACT CALLED THE DEALER SEVERAL TIMES AND WAS PLACED ON A WAITING LIST. THE MANUFACTURER WAS NOT MADE AWARE OF THE FAILURE. THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS UNKNOWN. PARTS DISTRIBUTION DISCONNECT.
